data.description: A brand new IBHS fortified roof will be installed prior to closing!! This home is bright and fresh, with vaulted ceilings and new finishes! Extensive updates were completed throughout in 2019, including replacing the home's two HVACs, installing new stainless-steel appliances, new LVP flooring throughout, new carpet in the upstairs loft and second floor bedroom, new granite, newly remodeled kitchen and bathrooms, new fixtures, new paint, a new fence, and a new water heater. Located on a quiet cul-de-sac in a wonderful neighborhood that is close to everything, this is the perfect family home. The living room, dining room, three of the four bedrooms, a large eat-in kitchen, and the laundry room are all on the main level. There is a sizable bonus loft and large, private one-bedroom suite upstairs with a full bath for guests or family. The entire downstairs, including all three full bathrooms, features new LVP flooring, and the kitchen features new granite countertops and new stainless-steel appliances. The best part is that this light, spacious kitchen overlooks a totally private outdoor entertaining oasis, which includes a patio with pergola and an in-ground family pool, all nestled within a private fenced backyard. With access to the newly opened Military Cut-off bypass, you are less than 6 miles from Wrightsville Beach, 3.5 miles from Mayfaire, and less than 8 miles from ILM!
